'From Small-Land 3.8-5976-0266 of 10 September 2004 [latest update: #5976] on 12 September 2004 at 8:47:42 pm'!"Change Set:		MorphIconOrThumbnail-dgdDate:			12 September 2004Author:			Diego Gomez DeckMethods for convenience to represent any morph as an icon or as a thumbnail of itself.Useful to put an representation of any morph on menus, docking bars, etc."!!Morph methodsFor: 'thumbnail' stamp: 'dgd 9/12/2004 20:19'!icon	"Answer a form with an icon to represent the receiver"	^ nil! !!Morph methodsFor: 'thumbnail' stamp: 'dgd 9/12/2004 20:33'!iconOrThumbnail	"Answer an appropiate form to represent the receiver"	^ self icon		ifNil: [ | maxExtent fb |maxExtent := 320 @ 240.			fb := self fullBounds.			fb area <= (maxExtent x * maxExtent y)				ifTrue: [self imageForm]				ifFalse: [self imageFormForRectangle: (fb topLeft extent: maxExtent)]		]! !